“为何人类对气候变化 其严重性毫无头绪？”

19
00:00:53.832 --> 00:00:56.540
"Why don't people know what's happening or how bad it is?
“应该有人告诉他们!”

20
00:00:56.540 --> 00:00:57.832
Someone should tell them!"
